{% doc %}
  @prompt
    The Sovereign Architecture
    1. Core Section Concept
    
    Create a highly customizable, 3-column "Pillars" section titled "THE 9 FOUNDATIONS." This section must visually represent Structural Grace—using generous white space, minimalist alignment, and high-contrast typography.
    2. Typography & Styling (Mandatory)
    
        Headings: Use Bodoni Moda (Serif) for a sense of timeless authority.
    
        Body Text: Use Manrope (Sans-Serif) for modern clarity.
    
        Colors: Provide color pickers for the background, headings, and body text.
    
        Mobile: Columns must stack gracefully into a single-column layout on mobile devices.
    
    3. Content Structure (The Trinity Framework)
    
    Column I: Internal Architecture
    
        Numeral: I (Lightweight Bodoni)
    
        Heading: Internal Architecture
    
        Description: Restoring the foundational bedrock of the leader’s core through the activation of original intent.
    
        The Foundation List: Original Design • Unshakeable Truth • The Peace of Sovereignty
    
    Column II: The Sovereign Mantle
    
        Numeral: II (Lightweight Bodoni)
    
        Heading: The Sovereign Mantle
    
        Description: Harmonizing spiritual authority with marketplace authenticity to carry influence without the weight of performance.
    
        The Foundation List: Structural Grace • The Language of Honor • Identity Stewardship
    
    Column III: Legacy Curation
    
        Numeral: III (Lightweight Bodoni)
    
        Heading: Legacy Curation
    
        Description: Extending global impact through generational systems and the strategic alignment of economic wisdom.
    
        The Foundation List: Economic Stewardship • Generational Echo • Unified Vision
    
    4. Interactive & Design Controls (The Schema)
    
    The AI must enable the following adjustments in the Shopify Theme Editor:
    
        Editable Text: Allow changes to all headings, numerals, descriptions, and list items.
    
        Sizing Sliders: Adjustable font sizes for the Main Title (H2), Column Titles (H3), and Body Copy.
    
        Spacing/Padding: Adjustable sliders for "Section Top/Bottom Padding" and "Column Gap."
    
        The Footer Note: Include a field for an italicized caption at the bottom: "These foundations are the structural grace upon which every Sovereign Mantle is built."
    
    5. Prophetic Note Styling
    
    Include a block at the end of the section for a Prophetic Calibration Note:
    
        Text: "These foundations are not a curriculum; they are a calibration. We do not build on top of old structures; we return to the original intent."
    
        Style: Centered, lightweight Manrope, with a subtle horizontal line above it., 1. Text Punctuation & Rhythm:
    
        In the 3 columns, update the bulleted lists at the bottom of each section. Replace the current punctuation with a clean middle dot • and ensure there is exactly one space before and after each dot.
    
            Example: Original Design • Unshakeable Truth • The Peace of Sovereignty
    
    2. Line Spacing (Structural Grace):
    
        Increase the Line Height (line spacing) for the two-sentence descriptions in each column to 1.8.
    
        Increase the Margin-Bottom of the Pillar Titles (e.g., "Internal Architecture") to 20px to create more breathing room between the title and the description.
    
    3. Prophetic Note Styling:
    
        For the final text block at the very bottom ("These foundations are not a curriculum..."):
    
            Increase the Font Weight by one level (or change color to a slightly darker charcoal) to ensure high legibility.
    
            Set the Font Style to Italic.
    
            Add 40px of Padding-Top to this specific block so it sits clearly away from the three columns above it.
    
    4. Global Font Check:
    
        Confirm all headings are strictly set to Bodoni Moda and all body/list text is strictly set to Manrope., Shopify AI Command: Vertical Pillar Alignment
    
    1. List Re-Formatting:
    
        Within the three pillars, remove the middle dots • from the foundation lists.
    
        Change the list layout from "inline" to a Vertical Stack (one foundation per line).
    
        Ensure the list is Left-Aligned to match the description text above it.
    
    2. Bullet Styling:
    
        Do NOT use standard round bullets. Use a Thin Horizontal Dash — or a simple Vertical Line | before each foundation to maintain the architectural feel.
    
        Example:
        — Original Design
        — Unshakeable Truth
        — The Peace of Sovereignty
    
    3. Spacing Fine-Tuning:
    
        Add 15px of space between the description paragraph and the start of the vertical list.
    
        Set the Line-Height for the list items to 1.6 so the foundations don't feel "cramped."
    
    4. Typography Check:
    
        Ensure the stacked list remains in Manrope, but set the font size to be slightly smaller (e.g., 2px smaller) than the description text above it to create a clear visual hierarchy. AND FOR THE PROPHETIC note text, increase the text shade one shade darker, Subtext Addition & Refinement
    
    1. Subtext Integration:
    
        Add a Subtext field directly beneath the main section title "THE 9 FOUNDATIONS."
    
        The Text: "A comprehensive blueprint designed to align internal magnitude with external authority."
    
        Position: Centered, directly below the H2 title.
    
    2. Subtext Typography (Manrope):
    
        Font Family: Set strictly to Manrope (Sans-Serif).
    
        Font Style: Regular or Lightweight (not bold).
    
        Font Size: Set to 18px (or roughly 30% smaller than the main title) to ensure clear hierarchy.
    
        Text Color: Use a slightly muted charcoal or deep grey (e.g., #4A4A4A) to distinguish it from the black title.
    
    3. "Quiet Luxury" Spacing:
    
        Top Margin: Add 10px of space between the Title and this Subtext.
    
        Bottom Margin: Add 40px of space between the Subtext and the start of the 3 Columns. This ensures the "Foundations" have room to breathe before the reader dives into the details.
    
    4. Final Consistency Check:
    
        Ensure the Section Background Color remains consistent with the Bio and Media sections.
    
        Ensure the Section Title (THE 9 FOUNDATIONS) remains in Bodoni Moda and is all-caps.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-sovereign-foundations-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__main-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Bodoni Moda', serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.main_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size }}px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtext_color }};
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__pillars-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.column_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.footer_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__numeral-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Bodoni Moda', serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.numeral_size }}px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.numeral_spacing }}px 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Bodoni Moda', serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.column_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_text_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 15px 0;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: calc({{ block.settings.body_text_size }}px - 2px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '—';
    margin-right: 10px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__footer-note-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.footer_note_size }}px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: {{ block.settings.footer_spacing }}px 0 0 0;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__prophetic-note-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.prophetic_spacing }}px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-sovereign-foundations__prophetic-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.prophetic_text_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.prophetic_text_color }};
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-sovereign-foundations__pillars-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.mobile_column_gap }}px;
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__main-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.main_title_size }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subtext_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__numeral-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.numeral_size }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.column_title_size }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.body_text_size }}px * 0.95);
    }

    .ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc(({{ block.settings.body_text_size }}px - 2px) * 0.95);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<sovereign-foundations-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-sovereign-foundations-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.main_title != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-sovereign-foundations__main-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.main_title }}
        </h2>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.subtext != blank %}
        <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.subtext }}
        </p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillars-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.pillar_1_numeral != blank %}
          <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__numeral-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_1_numeral }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_1_title != blank %}
          <h3 class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_1_title }}
          </h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_1_description != blank %}
          <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_1_description }}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_1_list != blank %}
          <ul class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign list_items = block.settings.pillar_1_list | split: '•' %}
            {% for item in list_items %}
              {% assign trimmed_item = item | strip %}
              {% if trimmed_item != blank %}
                <li class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ trimmed_item }}</li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.pillar_2_numeral != blank %}
          <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__numeral-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_2_numeral }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_2_title != blank %}
          <h3 class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_2_title }}
          </h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_2_description != blank %}
          <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_2_description }}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_2_list != blank %}
          <ul class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign list_items = block.settings.pillar_2_list | split: '•' %}
            {% for item in list_items %}
              {% assign trimmed_item = item | strip %}
              {% if trimmed_item != blank %}
                <li class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ trimmed_item }}</li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.pillar_3_numeral != blank %}
          <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__numeral-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_3_numeral }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_3_title != blank %}
          <h3 class="ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_3_title }}
          </h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_3_description != blank %}
          <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.pillar_3_description }}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.pillar_3_list != blank %}
          <ul class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% assign list_items = block.settings.pillar_3_list | split: '•' %}
            {% for item in list_items %}
              {% assign trimmed_item = item | strip %}
              {% if trimmed_item != blank %}
                <li class="ai-sovereign-foundations__list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ trimmed_item }}</li>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if block.settings.footer_note != blank %}
      <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__footer-note-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.footer_note }}
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.show_prophetic_note %}
      <div class="ai-sovereign-foundations__prophetic-note-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.prophetic_note != blank %}
          <p class="ai-sovereign-foundations__prophetic-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.prophetic_note }}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</sovereign-foundations-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class SovereignFoundations{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.initializeAccessibility();
      }

      initializeAccessibility() {
        const pillars = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-sovereign-foundations__pillar-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        pillars.forEach((pillar, index) => {
          pillar.setAttribute('role', 'article');
          pillar.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Foundation pillar ' + (index + 1));
        });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('sovereign-foundations-{{ ai_gen_id }}', SovereignFoundations{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

